Webinar broadcast date: Tuesday, 27 October 2020 13h00 GMT | 15h00 SAST Northern Ireland is home to a widespread pool of mining technology talent – that caters to helping build new generation mines across Africa.  When considering potential supply and service provider partners to deliver new-age technologies to enhance the performance of your mine – the region cannot be ignored. Join Mining Review Africa and Invest Northern Ireland as we unpack two areas within the mining sector that demonstrate the phenomenal successes Northern Irish companies can achieve on the continent. Join this session to learn: Speakers: Swathi Sri, Head of Territory, IMEA | Invest Northern IrelandWillem Du Plooy, Business Development Manager South Africa | CDE GlobalDavid Procter, Systems Development Manager | SensoteqSteve Gray, Country Manager – West Africa | UK Export Finance